tion</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRPose/position\"><code>position</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>timestamp</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for WebVR API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/displayId\"><code>Gamepad.displayId</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/activeVRDisplays\"><code>Navigator.activeVRDisplays</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getVRDisplays\"><code>Navigator.getVRDisplays()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRDisplayCapabilities\"><code>VRDisplayCapabilities</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRDisplayEvent\"><code>VRDisplayEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters\"><code>VREyeParameters</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRFieldOfView\"><code>VRFieldOfView</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRFrameData\"><code>VRFrameData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRLayerInit\"><code>VRLayerInit</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters\"><code>VRStageParameters</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>timestamp</code></strong>&nbsp;是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose\"><code>VRPose</code></a> 接口的只读属性，返回为系统此时的时间戳&nbsp;— 一个单调递增的数值，代表这个软件启动到现在的时间。</p>\n\n<p>这个属性对于确定位置数据是否已更新和什么次序更新了很有用。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myTimeStamp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> VRPose<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>timestamp<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMHighResTimeStamp\"><code>DOMHighResTimeStamp</code></a> 代表时间戳，以秒为单位。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">TBD.</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"about:unknown#dom-vrpose-timestamp\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">timestamp</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-\">Unknown</span></td>\n   <td>初始定义</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.VRPose.timestamp","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API homepage</a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"http://mozvr.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MozVr.com</a> — 来自于 Mozilla 的 VR 团队的模板、下载以及其他其他资源。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"timestamp 是 VRPose 接口的只读属性，返回为系统此时的时间戳 — 一个单调递增的数值，代表这个软件启动到现在的时间。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"VRPose.timestamp","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/vrpose/timestamp","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/vrpose/timestamp/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose","title":"VRPose"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/VRPose/timeStamp","title":"VRPose.timestamp"}],"pageTitle":"VRPose.timestamp - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}